626e6b53-2411-4128-ba55-a108ff9b9414.03601e55-9c7e-49d1-880b-fdb1294fae6e.description=failed to kill the process 626e6b53-2411-4128-ba55-a108ff9b9414.03601e55-9c7e-49d1-880b-fdb1294fae6e.prompt=failed to kill the process 626e6b53-2411-4128-ba55-a108ff9b9414.04f7de19-bb16-408d-bb7e-e4f945b8d0af.transition.description=Wait completed, checking to see if process successfully stopped. 626e6b53-2411-4128-ba55-a108ff9b9414.0f7a2945-1ae9-437e-acbb-838bd7ca789c.description=
This operation kills a process

Inputs\:
	host\:           host name to check
	username\:       user name to login into host as
	password\:       password to use for login
	PID\:            the PID of the process to kill

Responses\:
	Passed\:         If the file was deleted (return code was 0)
	Host Not Found\: If the host cannot be found
	Authentication Failure\: If the login fails
	Failed\:         Any other error condition

Results and Context\:
	The kill return code is placed into the operation result
	Nothing is placed into the context
626e6b53-2411-4128-ba55-a108ff9b9414.0f7a2945-1ae9-437e-acbb-838bd7ca789c.prompt=This Sample will demonstrate how to use the Kill Process operation to kill a proccess. 626e6b53-2411-4128-ba55-a108ff9b9414.37cc897b-aceb-4995-9d5a-fd73042db86b.description=
This operation verifies that a process with a particular PID exists

Inputs\:
	host\:            host name to check
	username\:        user name to login into host as
	password\:        password to use for login
	PID\:             the PID to check

Responses\:
	Running\:         If the process is running
	Not Running\:     If the process is not running
	Host Not Found\:  If the host cannot be found
	Authentication Failure\: If the login fails
	Failed\:          Any other error condition

Results and Context\:
	The ps return code is placed into the operation result
	Nothing is placed into the context
